print('external', Rext)

## Make a movie
import os
fig, ax = plt.subplots()
name = 'basinbetaForceverysub300inertialNoLayer'
try:
    os.mkdir(f'Movie{name}')
except:
    pass
with xr.open_dataset(f'{name}.snapshot.nc') as ds0:
    for t in range(ds0.sizes['Time'] ):
        ds = ds0.isel(Time=t)
        ax.clear()
        cs = ax.contour(ds.xt, ds.yt, ds.psi[:, :]*1000, levels=np.arange(-1e-1, 1e-1, 5e-3)*1000, linewidths=0.5)
        ax.pcolormesh(ds.xt, ds.yu, ds.v.isel(zt=1), vmin=-0.002, vmax=0.002, cmap='RdBu_r')
        ax.clabel(cs, fmt='%1.1f')
    
        ax.contour(ds.xt, ds.yt, np.abs(ds.surface_taux.values + ds.surface_tauy.values*1j), colors='0.7', levels = np.arange(0, 0.11, 0.05))
        ax.set_aspect(1)
        time = ds.Time.values.astype(float)/1e9/3600
        ax.set_title(time)
        fig.savefig(f'Movie{name}/Movie{name}{t:03d}.png')
